[Clearly the Australian government is interested in containment and
eradication of this disease. However, given the rapid spread of the
disease it would seem prudent on the government's part to be ordering
substantially more vaccine.
In addition to disease eradication economics seems to play on the
mind of most government officials. The racing industry has surely
entered into that equation. At least, one would hope so. - Mod.TG]
